snippet.title: Chuggington Mega Bloks Jet Pack Adventure Wilson - Unboxing and Review - 4 Layout Demo
snippet.description:
CHUGGINGTON MEGA BLOKS Jet Pack Adventure - Unboxing and Review - 4 Layout Demo

Blast-off to hours of chuggersonic adventure with Wilson and Action Chugger in this fast-paced CHUGGINGTON MEGA BLOKS Jet Pack Adventure Set! See Action Chugger and Wilson fly down the buildable sky-rail with their jet packs to see who will land first. Build and rebuild the iconic Clock Tower and Chuggington depo for loads of exciting action. Build the tracks through the buildings & ride the rails up to four levels high. With over 103 buildable pieces included in the set, the building possibilities are endless!    Combine with other Chuggington Mega Bloks characters and play sets to multiply the fun!

- Includes 4-part buildable Vee and 2 Chuggers: 8-part buildable Wilson and Action Chugger, both with mouth-movement for lots of fun!
- Cool buildable Jet-Pack for the Chuggers to fly through the customizable Sky-Rail!
- 2-in-1 Build and rebuild possibilities with a 4-storey Clock Tower and a 3-level train station!
- Build lots of different track configurations included in the playset!
- Hours of fun on its own or with other Mega Bloks Chuggington Construction sets.

Sells for US$45 - US$50 at Amazon, Walmart
Amazon: http://www.amazon.com/Mega-Bloks-Chuggington-Chuggers-Adventure/dp/B005CLQ18W/?tag=thewanfulworo-20

snippet.title: ЛЕГО Полиция Машины для Детей Распаковка Игрушек Хот Вилс | Toys Unboxing
snippet.description:
Игрушечный пудинг при перевозке автомашин хот вилс была остановлена полицией для проверки документов на машины. Полиция попросила распаковать все машины. Первая машинка хот вилс PASS N GASSER дебютировал 2008 году документы в порядке. Вторая машинка MUSCLE TONE легендарных машинок Hot Wheels, выпускающихся с 1968 года документы в порядке. И третья машинка хот вилс 68 COPO CAMARO документы в порядке! Можете ехать!!!

0:08 Хот вилс PASS N GASSER
1:35 Машинка MUSCLE TONE
3:08  Хот вилс 68 COPO CAMARO

snippet.title: Love to Hug Elmo Plush Sesame Street Toy Unboxing
snippet.description:
Join us for a Love to Hug Elmo Sesame Street Toy Unboxing! We love Sesame Street toys and we’re so happy that Sesame Street has  been on for 50 years and counting. The Love to Hug Elmo plush toy is so cute and cuddly and Christian was so happy because Elmo is his favorite Sesame Street character. It’s very special to be able to share a show I loved as a child with my kids. And we are big Sesame Street collectors, especially Christian’s older brother who has autism and  lives and breathes all things Sesame Street. We hope you enjoy this video and don't forget to smile! 😊

snippet.title: Clown Bingo and Cement Mixer Toy Unboxing
snippet.description:
Hi kids! Do you image that today Clown Bingo’s truck brought him the set of Cement Mixer? 
Clown Bom is delighted. He is showing you how the cement mixer works. This toy is made with high quality and it is very secure! It has a lot of functions like a real construction machine. 
The windshield, wheel, seats and the stick shift is made of plastic and the cabin leads forward to get to the engine. The trommel spins by the handle and the gutter opens up to the ground.
This machinery develops the kid’s logic, imagination and motor skills. Also visual perception and memory

This machinery develops the kid’s logic, imagination and motor skills. Also visual perception and memory
